Woman was hit over the head 20 times with a rock at a bus stop in Leeds . 
  She was dragged into a garden and left for dead after the attack last month . 
  Police have released CCTV footage of the man following three other women earlier that night . 
  He is wanted for rape and attempted murder and had already stalked three others . 
  The 18-year-old victim was left with serious head injuries and a broken hip . 
  Police said he was of Pakistani or Middle Eastern background and in his early twenties . 
 